%F A059029 Third main diagonal of A059026: a(n) = B(n+2, n) = lcm(n+2, n)/(n+2) + lcm(n+2, n)/n - 1 for all n >= 1.
%F A059029 a(2*n) + a(2*n+1) = A016945(n). - _Paul Curtz_, Aug 29 2008
